    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Note: The current demo is available in English only. Full language support will be included in the full release.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在分裂王国，政客们是名副其实的怪物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是吸血鬼强制要求民众在脖子上纹刻血液里的卡路里含量，还是僵尸一本正经地推行“步行限速”法令，这个国家所受的苦难分毫未减。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是时候迎来改变了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因为一旦你问鼎“兽相”之位，这个国家将以耳目一新且极其“精彩”的方式，再度承受苦难！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/4ec80afb2b10edf1e0f082374ce6e8d5.avif?t=1771952471\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras_big/4ec80afb2b10edf1e0f082374ce6e8d5.webp?t=1771952471 width=1560 height=229 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/de21c7f9a5cdd9cca313e2c3a622691b.poster.avif?t=1771952471\" width=960 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/de21c7f9a5cdd9cca313e2c3a622691b.webm?t=1771952471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/de21c7f9a5cdd9cca313e2c3a622691b.mp4?t=1771952471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在分裂王国的议会里，理性辩论根本没人在意！你可以肆意霸凌、勒索、威胁，甚至不惜大打出手，只为换取那一张张选票。而这，还仅仅是针对自家党派同僚的手段！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/625a9ab030d9097fe2a51560cb6f676c.avif?t=1771952471\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras_big/625a9ab030d9097fe2a51560cb6f676c.webp?t=1771952471 width=1560 height=229 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/bad58070ebe33b97828ab2c2406a076e.poster.avif?t=1771952471\" width=960 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/bad58070ebe33b97828ab2c2406a076e.webm?t=1771952471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/bad58070ebe33b97828ab2c2406a076e.mp4?t=1771952471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >公开诺斯费拉图档案？纵火去罪化？同“咒”婚姻合法化？终于，你大权在握，可以将你那套令人发指的政策议程，强加给这个早已精疲力竭的国家！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/c4ca49867a1c64bef7dc3fff10a03135.avif?t=1771952471\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras_big/c4ca49867a1c64bef7dc3fff10a03135.webp?t=1771952471 width=1560 height=229 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/7d418274c98a751512a8b2a4cbd138ea.poster.avif?t=1771952471\" width=960 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/7d418274c98a751512a8b2a4cbd138ea.webm?t=1771952471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/7d418274c98a751512a8b2a4cbd138ea.mp4?t=1771952471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是拒绝为你那黑料满满的陈年推文低头认错、坦然收下军火商递来的免费样机，还是对自己的管家狂喷催泪瓦斯，毕竟你才是大佬，一切由你定夺。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/22088009c141c688509dc528008ac093.avif?t=1771952471\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras_big/22088009c141c688509dc528008ac093.webp?t=1771952471 width=1560 height=229 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/f75ccf66883dfa21db39782d35ff60f9.poster.avif?t=1771952471\" width=960 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/f75ccf66883dfa21db39782d35ff60f9.webm?t=1771952471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/f75ccf66883dfa21db39782d35ff60f9.mp4?t=1771952471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来自 15 个政党的 30 名面目可憎的党派代表已严阵以待，准备疯狂蚕食你的理念与政策，甚至连你的长相也不会放过！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/6e3f9380c28603ef9135cc00f9746bc2.avif?t=1771952471\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras_big/6e3f9380c28603ef9135cc00f9746bc2.webp?t=1771952471 width=1560 height=229 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/04e0be6b254adab45bbed1dce8d05cf5.poster.avif?t=1771952471\" width=960 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/04e0be6b254adab45bbed1dce8d05cf5.webm?t=1771952471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/04e0be6b254adab45bbed1dce8d05cf5.mp4?t=1771952471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一张卡牌都是一次抉择：你可以规规矩矩地发动牌面效果（真没创意！），也可以像任何一位合格的政客那样，榨取卡牌价值，将其转化为政治资本，从而施展你那强横的个人权术。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/272395ff31cff0830f629198a17b518a.avif?t=1771952471\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras_big/272395ff31cff0830f629198a17b518a.webp?t=1771952471 width=1560 height=229 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/8332a1298500dcbef96a14395ecc38df.poster.avif?t=1771952471\" width=960 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/8332a1298500dcbef96a14395ecc38df.webm?t=1771952471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/8332a1298500dcbef96a14395ecc38df.mp4?t=1771952471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是崇尚暴力的政坛悍将、卑劣圆滑的政治无赖，还是无可救药的政治蠢材？三类经典的政坛面孔任你扮演：兽工党的砍爷巴德斯顿、吸血胜选党的索沃思子爵，以及僵化人民运动的罗缇尔达·德·凯。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/5e927e43c173027b76d1b7cb24238f0d.avif?t=1771952471\" width=91 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/fcc57298c68ed9c9670cd926747e3647.avif?t=1771952471\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras_big/fcc57298c68ed9c9670cd926747e3647.webp?t=1771952471 width=1560 height=229 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >民众渴求着你无力负担的东西，党派索要着你注定无法实现的承诺，而你的对手只想置你于死地。若想守住权力，你必须设法维持你的个人威望、政治资本、民调支持率以及经费储备。祝你好运！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/6bd2217a131c93c09be52d62560c258b.avif?t=1771952471\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras_big/6bd2217a131c93c09be52d62560c258b.webp?t=1771952471 width=1560 height=229 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >辩论理应讲求尊重与体面，对吧？大错特错！在这里，如果你不喜欢对手的发言，大可以直接让他永远闭嘴。当然，前提是千万别被那位议院咆哮议长逮个正着！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/d2a024288d2f922592cd2f492b4fe224.avif?t=1771952471\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras_big/d2a024288d2f922592cd2f492b4fe224.webp?t=1771952471 width=1560 height=229 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >向轻信的选民许下荒唐承诺，亲手拉高生存难度。这不过是你为强留政治遗产所进行的一次注定走偏的尝试。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras/c3199d9f026efdc5619fa0a900783361.avif?t=1771952471\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214480/extras_big/c3199d9f026efdc5619fa0a900783361.webp?t=1771952471 width=1560 height=229 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的政治生涯是否就像小丑勇闯雷区，只不过，一点都不好笑？你的党派是否已对你心灰意冷？不如先发制人，主动请辞，以一个彻头彻尾失败者的姿态卷铺盖走人！</p>",
